Author: lylya75
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐️⭐️⭐️COFFE - The platform for the management of crypto assets ⭐️⭐️⭐️
Body: The consensus of delegated proof of stake (DPOS)  is a process of agreeing of a certain order of transactions, and filter of invalid transactions1. The only known decentralized consensus algorithm that is proven can satisfy the requirements to the productivity of applications on blockchain (speed, scalability, etc.) is the algorithm of delegated proof-of-stake (DPOS)2.  According to this algorithm, blockchain token holders trust to the block producers (“Block-Producers”, “delegated trust nodes”) to confirm the transaction exactly the same as the Bitcoin holders trust to confirm transactions to the miners. Producers are selected through a system of continuous random distribution. Any producer in the system can get the right to create the blocks, and after the creation of a block, he again gets in the queue among the other producers.  The right to confirm has all producers of network (Block-Producers), whose are the owners of large packages of COFFE tokens (including the projects realized on the COFFE ICO Standard platform), but not miners. This means the absence of competition for the highest commission to confirm. It means a constant price of commission (if it is provided), as well as the possibility of deployment in the COFFE blockchain the decentralized applications working without commissions at all.  Visit the site https://coffe.io/ to know more.

Author: lylya75
Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐️⭐️⭐️COFFE - The platform for the management of crypto assets ⭐️⭐️⭐️
Body: A feature of the COFFE platform is the realization of a system of mutual inter-user P2P (“person-to-person”) rewards for the using of tools and services of the COFFE platform. The funds for this system are formed from the share of all commissions received by the COFFE platform, which are accumulated on a special account (wallet), from which the self-executing contract (smart contract) redistributes them to users. The special account (wallet) itself is controlled and managed in a decentralized way – by delegated trust nodes. The decision about the distribution of funds is accepted by a vote of the nodes of delegated trust.  To participate in the system of mutual inter-user P2P (“person-to-person”) rewards for the using of tools and services of the COFFE platform, each member of system during the registration on the COFFE platform must give an approval: • to receive rewards for using the tools and services of the COFFE platform from other members of the COFFE platform and • to pay rewards for using the tools and services of the COFFE platform to other members of the COFFE platform.  Visit the site https://coffe.io/ to know more.

It did not look like an unsolvable problem, but its solution required a coordinated and harmonious scheme of all elements of the project. There was no time to understand in detail and optimize a large number of drafts written by different team members at different times. In our growing team we have found an excellent specialist in the technical description of projects. From the chaos of our ideas, but not without the help of almost all of our team, he designed the first version of White Paper.  Having done the work professionally, binding all our raw materials and ideas into a single logical decision, he gave us an excellent basis for the further work. Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐️⭐️⭐️COFFE - The platform for the management of crypto assets ⭐️⭐️⭐️
Body: Blockchain  I have nothing against the mining and the PoW algorithm for the confirmation of transactions in blockchain, but from the beginning this technology did not take a root ideologically in our project. For the illusory “increase of the value of records in the distributed register” the users of blockchain pay the commissions to a huge number of fans of simple solutions (mining farms), spending the computing power and energy on the tasks that can be successfully solved without them, using much less resources. The proof-of-stake (PoS) algorithm is, in my opinion, a much more advanced technology, but it also has the weakness to impose the payments for the blockchain on ordinary users in the form of network fees.  We expect the blockchain to be more simple and practical. In our coordinate system, the main place is given not to the miner / producer / validator and his desires, but to an ordinary user of the blockchain — an investor, a programmer, an ideologist, an expert and a beginner — from any sphere of activity. We don’t think outside of crypto sphere, but we think the “crypto sphere”. Crypto sphere must be convenient and useful to the common man.  We have identified the project EOSIO based on the DPoS algorithm for many reasons (this is a separate big question and we do not speak about it now). The free license and open source gave us the opportunity to make a legal fork of the EOS blockchain and start the practical implementation of our idea. We began a painstaking and very time-consuming process. But we had the main thing — a team of like-minded professionals: the ideologists, programmers, designers and marketers. And although there were no professionals among us in the field of “presentation”/ ”sale” of blockchain projects, we did not need them at that time. We decided: first the product, and everything else will be later.  You can get more information at the site https://coffe.io/

Body: Exchange  After we worked out the basis for the functioning of the PACK and the relationship between the Expert and investors, we were faced by the question: will we be interested for the existing crypto exchanges with such a product? Almost all of them have a completely different purpose of their existence. For them the quality of work is not important. The most important is the number of transactions. “The exchange is always in the plus”, because it has become a “pump”, in the form of commissions pumping the liquidity from the wallets of many players to its own wallet. Hence the stimulation of active trade and transactions, no matter what is the result for traders. We know the result, don’t we?  Of course, our goal would not be interesting to exchanges and, of course, we decided to build our own exchange, adapted to our main idea. Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐️⭐️⭐️COFFE - The platform for the management of crypto assets ⭐️⭐️⭐️
Body: Manage not managing  PACK is designed for the non-professional participants who can evaluate the effectiveness of the Expert based on his rating in the system and the approximate expected level of profitability transferring their funds in the PACK. These participants delegate to the Expert the right to decide professionally when to close the positions in case of unfavorable market conditions of the assets that component the PACK.  The Expert can work with all assets that component the PACK, placing BID/ASK orders, conditional orders, use the leverage and the trading robot integrated into the system. The Expert does not have a right to withdraw the assets and use any fraudulent schemes.  A non-professional participant buys a share in PACK after it is formed by the Expert and put on the auction. After purchase he becomes an investor of PACK. The sale of PACK is done in real time, as well as the sale on any other exchange market.  The Expert receives the funding and shares the risks with non-professional investors. He receives a reward as a percentage of the total profit of the PACK at the time of its closure.  The investor can sell his share in PACK to other market participants at any time.  You can get more information at the site https://coffe.io/

Body: News from facebook  Choice and trust  Of course, the choice of assets is a fundamental moment and, ideally, it should be done by a professional expert of the crypto market. But why would an Expert share his or her knowledge or experience with the non-professional participants? And how to ensure the trust of non-professional participants in the selection of an expert?  The answer to the first question is simple — “the benefit”, and not only financial. First, the PACK gives the opportunity to sell the expert’s competence to a wide range of unlimited players. In fact, through the PACK, the Expert provides the non-professional investors with a professional asset management service (most of the investors have such assets and they “do not work”) and gets payment for his work. At the same time, the Expert, attracting the funds to the management, receives a greater resource and the possibility of greater gross earnings. Second, the best results are demonstrated by the Expert, the higher is his verified status in the cryptosphere.  The trust is built on two things: an objective transparent evaluation of the Expert’s competencies as a manager and the Expert’s personal motivation to manage effectively. An objective public evaluation of an expert is his / her rating in the management system. A rating is an independent integrated evaluation. It is automatically calculated from the rates of return of portfolios (PACK) under the control of an Expert for a certain period. It depends from the ratio of successful deals to unsuccessful (adjusted for market state in general), etc. This rating is the basis for guide for non-professional participants and investors in the choice of the Expert.  Personal motivation for the effective management of the Expert arises only if the Expert risks by his own capital. Expert is the architect of PACK, participating in his own tool. The Expert is the same investor of the PACK created by him, together with the other participants, whose funds he additionally attracts under his management. He studies the market, clearly distinguishes the horizons of events, sees the dynamics of projects, clearly represents the immediate prospects, because he is a professional.  You can get more information at the site https://coffe.io/

Body: News from facebook  Who we are  In our small circle of like-minded people on one of the trading platforms, in the course of long discussions and heated disputes, often passing to the individuals, finally “ripe” the right idea. The idea of the PACK tool that would minimize the risk of working with a separate crypto assets for a professional and non-professional player. PACK is a “multi-asset “- a set of several assets that a professional investor packs into a single ”mini-portfolio” and offers to the market. PACK at the same time is accessible and understandable to any person, regardless of the level of competence. The point is that the sharp volatility of any individual asset included in the PACK, works on the growth of the entire portfolio, and the sharp decline in the value of an individual asset is compensated by the growth of others. The main question is: how to choose the promising assets and who can be trusted to do it.  You can get more information at the site https://coffe.io/

Body: News from facebook  For whom is COFFE?  If you have the pleasure to belong to a not-so-numerous community of crypto market experts and professional crypto traders, then you definitely know more than two thousand crypto assets that are currently on the market. You can with assumptions but in general correctly evaluate the market prospects of these assets on the basis of technical and fundamental analysis, to distinguish the scam project from the beginning. You can certainly easily use several trading platforms to reduce risks and increase the return on the market. And probably you can use the automated trading systems (trading robots) and algorithmic trading to automate the most operations. Body: News from facebook  The system of valuation of the potential and risks of COFFE Protocol  COFFE Protocol (“Confirmation of the Fact of Financial Evaluation“) is a system of valuation of potential and risks of the assets already exists on the market, as well as new assets – ICO (ITO) projects from the stage of idea to the readiness stage of entering the market.  The automated system makes a fundamental analysis of both the asset on the market and the new project. It collects and analyzes the data and / or makes the valid comparisons by analogues. The evaluation uses 8 factors and 60 criterias, among them are strategic positioning, technology of the blockchain, product, etc.  As a result, the system gives an evaluation that is used by: (1) Experts for the technical analysis of crypto asset and • the realization of effective strategies for the management of assets in the set of PACK, in COFFE Asset Management, • the formation of a promising crypto currency tools for Index Top COFFE. (2) Analysts to work with new ICO projects on the COFFE ICO Standard platform.  The system also analyzes the models of management by iPACK tools and on its basis assigns the ratings to Experts. The most effective Experts are involved in the asset management in COFFE Asset Management.  COFFE has launched a demo version of the platform. This is a link: https://dashboard.coffe.io/

Title: [ANN][ICO] ⭐️⭐️⭐️COFFE - The platform for the management of crypto assets ⭐️⭐️⭐️
Body: News from facebook  iPack  Startups bring the highest potential profit to the investor, but it is possible to invest not only in startups on our platform. Tools iPack allow relatively safe to invest in any crypto assets traded in the system. The idea is that the management of iPack is entrusted to professional traders, experts in this field, whose skills are confirmed by the real transactions and the rating is determined by the COFFE Protocol. All investments are made only on terms of investment.  Each expert managing the iPack invests in it at least 30% of his own funds. It increases his responsibility and reduces the risks. This management is not trust, as the expert can not withdraw the funds from iPack at his own decision. He can do it only by selling the assets and distributing them among the depositors, in the proportion to their investments. There are still many risks associated with the dishonesty of the expert. The system monitors his actions in the real time and analyzes the possible options for fraudulent actions. In case of emergency (the deals of expert coincide with one of the template of fraudulent actions), the system will block the transaction immediately. In the case of suspicion (if the template matches partially) the system will signal a specialist who has the ability to analyze the situation and also has the right to block the expert’s transactions.  More information at https://coffe.io/

Body: Facebook news  COFFE ICO Standard platform  The new technological solution provides both the protection of investors from the unfair projects on the one hand, and giving a start and financing to the perspective projects on the other. The platform is based on the global market of ideas, which allows to select the most promising of them for implementation, the decision of which is made by the collective intelligence of experts in the field of ICO. Experts who vote for a particular project with their own money have a fundamentally different level of responsibility. After making a preliminary decision, the project pass a comprehensive examination whis is paid from the funds paid by the owner of the idea during the placement of it in the catalog of the market or by the investors who have trust the idea of the project.  Verification of the project is done in several stages — technical expertise, examination of the economic model of the project, examination of the niche at the market and competitors. The conclusion is published in the public access, according to the results of this conclusion is done the initial financing of the project by funds of experts 30% and by funds of the system 70%.  For projects receiving the initial funding, immediately are connected the mechanisms for the preparation of the project to the ICO. The project has the opportunity to get all the necessary specialists immediately, based on the rating and feedback from the previous projects, the success of previous projects. The team chooses the specialists that allows to implement the ideas in the shortest possible time.  More information at https://coffe.io/

Body: Intelligent COFFE Protocol  The COFFE Protocol is intelligence of COFFE ecosystem. The COFFE Protocol provides the market with the indicators on the basis of which the traders choose an asset. The COFFE Protocol is a complex work on processing a huge amount of data related to crypto assets. It is a huge responsibility, since the financial result of all participants of the system depends on the decisions made by the intelligence of the Protocol. The Protocol is a living mechanism, constantly developing and growing with the system.  We cannot guarantee the infallibility of its work, but we can guarantee that the Protocol will be constantly developing and improving. Thanks to the Protocol, each crypto asset, including the derivatives, receives its own reliability indicator, each trader receives its own rating based on both his activity and the results of his work. The COFFE Protocol does not know how to predict the future. It simply provides the traders and crypto-investors with the objective data that allows them to make decisions. For today the degree of readiness of the Protocol is about 30%. It requires the large amounts of statistical data not only about crypto assets, but also about the work of traders in the COFFE system. It is planned to launch and pre-configure the Protocol no earlier than in 6 months after the launch of the COFFE Exchange in the operational mode.  Any member of the COFFE ecosystem becomes a neuron of the COFFE network.  More information at https://coffe.io/

Body: Unique tool — derivatives Pack  Pack derivatives are one of the most important components of the whole system, even more, it is its foundation. We will talk about the derivatives more than once or twice. In short, the Pack is a set of crypto assets, which together create a more stable and profitable asset, reduce the risks, since the fall of one asset is compensated by the growth of others. Pack is not an index, each Pack is unique because it contains an arbitrary number of arbitrary assets.  Using the Pack you can pay for a product or service, or send a Pack to any user of the COFFE network with an unlimited number of different cryptocurrencies by one click.  In order to choose the assets to form the Pack, it is necessary to correctly evaluate each asset on the market separately. For this purpose, an Intelligent COFFE Protocol is created.  More information at https://coffe.io/

All parts of the system are being designed and developed with the aim of improving the work of each member of the community from private investor to the professional trader, by reducing the costs of startups and existing established business-projects wishing to receive funding according to the principles of the ICO/ITO.  Elements of the system are a protective mechanism for investors from unfair projects. Fraudulent (scam) projects remain outside of the open window of opportunities, which includes only the best, most interesting and economically reasonable ideas. All elements of the system are instruments for the financing of fair and promising projects with the maximum protection of both investors and project creators. Body: On the official site of COFFE and at COFFE platform was installed a SSL certificate.  Now you can visit us at https://coffe.io/  and our platform at https://dashboard.coffe.io/  SSL Certificates provide secure, encrypted communications between a website and an internet browser. SSL stands for Secure Sockets Layer, the protocol which provides the encryption. SSL Certificates are typically installed on pages that require end-users to submit sensitive information over the internet like credit card details or passwords.  An SSL Certificate (Secure Sockets Layer), also called a Digital Certificate, creates a secure link between a website and a visitor's browser. By ensuring that all data passed between the two remains private and secure, SSL encryption prevents hackers from stealing private information such as credit card numbers, names and addresses.

Body: Blockchain COFFE Chain is a blockchain of “3rd generation”, which is based on Graphene technology.  The algorithm is based on the new principle of proof of ownership, by consensus of delegated proof of stake (DPOS). ”Technically" the COFFE Chain blockchain is a "fork" of the EOS blockchain. Figuratively speaking, if EOS is an advanced "technology“, freely distributed and non - commercial, then COFFE is a” product" with its own business model, independent, self-developing network and ecosystem that ensure its rapid development based on market incentives. The choice of independent development of COFFE Chain is dictated by the considerations and logic of rapid scaling of the business model of the COFFE platform.  More information at http://coffe.io/
